edu.stanford.nlp.sequences

Interface ListeningSequenceModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SequenceListener, SequenceModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CRFCliqueTree, EmpiricalNERPriorBIO, EntityCachingAbstractSequencePriorBIO

    public interface ListeningSequenceModel
extends SequenceModel, SequenceListener
    This is simply a conjunctive interface for something that is a SequenceModel and a SequenceListener. This is useful to have because models used in Gibbs sampling have to implement both these interfaces.
    Author:
    Christopher Manning
